          "id": "tldr-web-dev:2023-05-17:o007",
          "order": 1,
          "title": "CHATHUB",
          "summary": "ChatHub is an all-in-one chatbot client that allows you to use different chatbots in one app. It supports ChatGPT, Bing Chat, Google Bard, and Claude. It is full-featured with a shortcut to quickly activate the app from anywhere in the browser, a prompt library for custom and community prompts, dark mode, import/export options, conversation sharing, and more.",
