          "order": 3,
          "title": "BUN V0.6",
          "summary": "Bun is a fast all-in-one JavaScript runtime, built for speed, with a native bundler, transpiler, test runner, and npm-compatible package manager baked-in. Bun v0.6 is the biggest release of Bun yet. It has a new JavaScript/TypeScript bundler and minifier, a new ability to create standalone executables, and more.",
